content.rendered:
Who we are…

About Us

We are in the business of creating memories. We have a talented pool of creatives to guarantee you the most creative photography services in Kenya for both your social and corporate needs.

Our mantra reads:

  • Creative Photography; not stopping until it blows our minds
  • Quality images; our quality means that we shall stick to providing lasting, professional photography services in Kenya.
  • Memorable photography; worth coming back for more
  • Prompt: Just when you need it.

We are a registered photography company based in Nairobi: Westlands, Westpark Suites, Ojijo Road, where we have a state of art, spacious studio with the perfect environment to guarantee you professional photography services in Kenya.

“…I love our clients and enjoy developing relationships with them. There is nothing more satisfying than being able to capture a fun couple with the new-engagement butterflies, a beautiful bride and groom exchanging teary-eyed vows on their wedding day, a new born baby with the bliss they bring to the world, or just being there to celebrate you while you keep winning at the market place”

– Charles Ngomo: Lead Creative
